226 (c) The benefits provided by this section shall be the
227 same as benefits provided for dependents as described in
228 Chapter 6, Title 31, Code of Alabama 1975.
229 (d) The educational benefits authorized pursuant to
230 this section shall expire on December 31, 2028, unless
231 extended by an act of the Legislature.
